{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assume the role of Autonomous Strategic Mobile Projectile No. 100 (hereinafter referred to as &quot;No. 100&quot;) and strive to conquer the Facility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How to Navigate the Floors:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355900/extras/FIREBALL_gif-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1738704715\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Touch the black objects to charge energy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In this state, press the button to build power and release to launch toward the pointer.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(You can launch up to two times with a single charge.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Progress to the next area by leaping between black objects.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Once you reach the goal area, launch No. 100 into the goal to clear the floor.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">NOTE:Some floors may differ from these rules. Adapt as needed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize various gimmicks and physical laws to conquer each floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Clear all 15 floors within the time limit to conquer the Facility.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;If you conquer the Facility, I will grant you one wish.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;I want to see the outside world.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No. 100\u2019s challenge begins now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355900/page_bg_generated_v